"{\"uid\": \"bernews.com-2024-08-jah-nhai-perinchief-olympic-debut\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"[Written byStephen Wright]  Jah-Nhai Perinchiefsaid he feels grateful to become an Olympian and hopes to build on his debut showing as he looks towards the next chapter of his triple jump career.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 195, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 83, \"end\": 91, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9994272597532936, \"rank\": 0.0005730682393979004, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Perinchief -\\u00a0the first Bermudian to represent the island in track and field at the Olympics since 2016 - finished thirteenth in group A of the qualifiers today [August 7] with a best leap of 16.23 metres.\", \"from\": 197, \"to\": 401, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 220, \"end\": 229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermuda\", \"score\": 0.999999245851143, \"rank\": 5.24266258260088e-07, \"text\": \"Bermudian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermuda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermuda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jah-Nhai Perinchief on the big\\u00a0screen ahead of his first jump    The 26-year-old, who has suffered hamstring issues over the past few years, believes the best is yet to come and said he has relished every moment of his Olympic experience.\", \"from\": 403, \"to\": 641, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am definitely grateful to be here,\\\" Perinchief told Bernews.\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 706, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 698, \"end\": 705, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bernews\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bernews\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bernews\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bernews\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have had to battle my injuries to get to the Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 765, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The experience has been great, seeing so many great athletes at the Olympic Village.\\\"\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 853, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Competing in a packed Stade de France in Paris\\u00a0where the Bermuda flag was among those displayed inside the stadium, he had\\u00a0Brian Wellman, one of the island's greatest track and field athletes, offering him advice between jumps.\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 1082, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 877, \"end\": 892, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}, {\"begin\": 896, \"end\": 901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999231019986, \"rank\": 7.68979477773378e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 912, \"end\": 919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermuda\", \"score\": 0.999997576004471, \"rank\": 1.7534475569369755e-06, \"text\": \"Bermuda\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermuda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermuda\"}, {\"begin\": 978, \"end\": 991, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_Wellman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brian Wellman\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_Wellman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_Wellman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I felt good, felt ready, felt in shape,\\\" Perinchief said.\", \"from\": 1084, \"to\": 1142, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I missed a couple of my approach phases, which would have set me up to be in the final.\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1231, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I fouled my first jump by a centimetre and that would have got me through to the final. \\\"\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1323, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Perinchief -\\u00a0a Commonwealth Games medalist - said he is even more determined to return to the biggest stage when the next Olympics rolls into Los Angeles in 2028.\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1487, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1340, \"end\": 1358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2002_Commonwealth_Games\", \"score\": 0.9966000428592832, \"rank\": 0.0032010214224953257, \"text\": \"Commonwealth Games\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2002_Commonwealth_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2002_Commonwealth_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 1467, \"end\": 1478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999807355373175, \"rank\": 1.0943897551793676e-05, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The next four years could be big,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1534, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I know they will be.\", \"from\": 1535, \"to\": 1556, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I will make sure of it.\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1580, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Triple jump is a process and I have got time.\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1628, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am approaching my peak years.\\\"\", \"from\": 1629, \"to\": 1661, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bernews will be providing comprehensive coverage of Bermuda's athletes in the coming weeks.\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1758, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1719, \"end\": 1726, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermuda\", \"score\": 0.999997576004471, \"rank\": 1.7534475569369755e-06, \"text\": \"Bermuda\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermuda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermuda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"#2024Olympics#Jah-NhaiPerinchief#Olympics  Category:All,News,Sports  Trackback URL|Comments RSS Feed  Once again, go Jah-Nhai Perinchief!\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1897, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Archives:  Categories:  Tags:  Bernews\", \"from\": 1899, \"to\": 1937, \"entities\": []}]}"